author: Bapt-tech
long_description:
# RandomTP
## The Random teleport mod allow you to place your owns /rtp places to manage the player's spawnpoint.
Type the /rtp command in the chat to be tped to a semi-random place.
Change the places in the init.lua file !
Join the Discord to ask, get anwsers and warn about a bug ! [Mod Discord](https://discord.com/invite/mbyK4tJJ)
name: rtp
short_description: creates /rtp command and allow you to create your owns random teleport places
